'''''Starlog Communications International''''' was the publisher of the science fiction magazines [[Starlog (magazine)|''Starlog'']] and [[Starlog (magazine)|''Starlog Yearbook'']] that featured several behind-the-scenes articles and interviews about various aspects of the ''Star Wars'' franchise.

It also released ''[[The Official Star Wars Technical Journal]]'' magazines, the ''[[Star Wars Technical Journal]]'' compilation and ''[[Star Wars Technical Journal Collector's Edition]]''.

